replies.bodyText:
I don't mind strings, because that's what they're called in Android and we already have the context of permissions given the @Permission annotation.
@Permission(strings = { Manifest.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAGE, Manifest.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE }, alias = "publicStorage")
^ This looks good to me. 😁

